Comment: My name is Fred Mcgriff, and I'm a retired Baseball professional.

Having just "read" The Safest Sicilian by Alexander Delchev with Semko Semkov, I am ready to bring my new knowledge to battle.  The hilarity that ensues will be my woeful regurgitation of this fine GM teaching.
With this move I complete the book's subtitle, "A Black Repertoire with 1.e4 c5 2.nf3 e6"  Now I am ready to export some pain.  I feel almost omniscient.

oh no you didnt!
